    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require schools to have separate toilets for boys and girls",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "We want the Government to require schools to maintain the provision of girls and boys separate toilets. We believe that having boys and girls use the same toilet deprives students of the privacy they need. This is especially important for girls who have started menstruating.",
